data.description: This beautiful, lovingly maintained 4 bedroom, 2 bath pool home in the highly desirable Shingle Creek Reserve is ready for you to call your own! Make your way past the manicured front lawn to the inviting covered & screen enclosed front porch, which offers a comfortable outdoor space to relax and enjoy your morning coffee. Stepping through the front door, you are greeted by a bright and spacious foyer featuring a stunning and unique mural. Continue through to the massive great room with its coffered tray ceilings, and the open concept kitchen which offers an abundance of upgrades including gleaming granite counters, glass tile backsplash, all stainless steel appliances, under cabinet lighting, striking cappuccino colored solid wood cabinets, built-in wine refrigerator, walk-in pantry, and a massive working center island with a large farmhouse sink, counter-height breakfast bar, and beautiful pendant lighting. Nestled alongside the kitchen is the dining area with several large windows which allow plenty of natural light to stream into the home and flow throughout the spacious open floorplan. A generous bonus flex room is located on the other side of the kitchen, offering a space that can be designed to your needs, be that a home office, play room, home theatre, gym, an extra bedroom, or anything! The oversized master bedroom features a private en-suite bath with his-and-hers sinks, a walk-in shower with dual showerheads, linen closet, separate water closet, and a massive walk-in closet with custom built-in shelving. The remaining bedrooms share the second full bath which offers a dual sink vanity and separate water closet with a shower/tub combo. A full size laundry room with utility sink completes the interior of the home. A set of sliding glass doors from the great room leads out to the covered & screen enclosed rear patio, but that's not where this outdoor oasis ends. Beyond this comfortable sitting area there is a pavered patio with a large covered pergola, custom built outdoor bar, large above-ground pool, and a shed for extra storage. This fantastic outdoor living space, perfect for hosting friends and family, is sure to delight all your guests! Located in beautiful Shingle Creek Reserve at The Oaks, you will also have access to everything this community has to offer, including parks, trails, playground, picnic areas, basketball court, community dock and boat ramp, and more! Just minutes from many shopping and dining options in the popular Loop Kissimmee and Old Town, and only a short drive to all of Orlando's World-Famous attractions, as well as easy highway access via the 417, I-4, and Florida Turnpike, this turn-key, move in ready home with all the bells and whistles is one you don't want to miss! Call today for your private tour!
